{"tid":520151,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次去男朋友屋企食飯，應唔應該幫手洗碗？","createTime":"2018-01-05T06:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T10:09:01.000Z","uid":76318,"like":153,"dislike":594,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"8a821664023d45857917931c99d8baca1c87ab6c","tid":520151,"uid":76318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"事緣係我有個男仔friend係度話佢女朋友第一次上佢屋企食飯，食完飯就叫工人姐姐唔好洗等佢洗。<br />\n咁我就同男朋友講起呢件事，<br />\n男朋友: 啱呀，梗係要啦，你女人黎架嘛，咁樣賢良淑德啲。<br />\n我: 你邀請我上去你屋企食飯，過門都係客，你唔係叫客人洗碗呀？我食完幫手拎啲碗筷入去就得。<br />\n<br />\n正評: 應該啦屌，洗碗係女人既職責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評: 而家係女朋友定工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50ce44a4c4538e0f93d2e8b38d8077146c5bcb3","tid":520151,"uid":21462,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"如果你係港女格=正評"},{"pid":"17cba5c37365bb97d96d87a15571f974e515a4d9","tid":520151,"uid":16061,"like":147,"dislike":12,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"哦 當你係客 唔洗當你自己人"},{"pid":"db6d279f607ac118d657130ff377f6ab527eb9fc","tid":520151,"uid":165482,"like":71,"dislike":8,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"突登搶黎洗好做作喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f71e5602b23ea23eebe7d43cbd081147785bc21","tid":520151,"uid":142964,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"第一次，或頭幾次，其他人洗都ok....到自己同對方屋企熟左，可以幫手洗下<br />\n<br />\n前度成日係自己屋企幫手洗碗，但黎我屋企就係客....冇乜必要突登幫手...<br />\n<br />\n不過未熟到卡分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b483e6a97334008b8a6f39b5b715aa52226c2991","tid":520151,"uid":25179,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"你都識講過門都係客 一日未嫁都唔算家人"},{"pid":"d773a1c8a5d5a50c0a24c608ac1af13b4a0c19c7","tid":520151,"uid":89514,"like":3,"