果上去咪算 第時結左婚慌冇得妳洗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"I fucking know that feel"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"洗開碗第時有啲咩家族聚會好多人嚟食飯or整好多餸就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之男朋友唔洗 我都唔會洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友煮比我食我就會洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a7e892ad4a83df8085de6c85a6db649554e773","tid":520151,"uid":76318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有工人就幫手執下碗都可以<br />\n如果無工人係伯母負責洗嘅你扮下野講句你洗<br />\n通常伯母都會叫你唔洗啦出去坐 但已經加左分好過你食完野大支野咁坐響度un un腳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger 之前去ex屋企食飯，有工人姐姐洗碗我次次都會執入去俾佢，執到ex媽咪叫我唔好執。<br />\n如果係auntie洗既梗係點都入去抹下碗吹下水搏加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04dc52917c6aeccec80b4914131a22d014449d0","tid":520151,"uid":76318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港女人連煎隻蛋都唔撚識 就算扮到第一次之後又咪穿煲 除非本身條女本身真係賢妻良母 否則點解要洗呢 棧搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我好中意洗碗，但係唔會第一次見面就幫你洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熟左間唔中都ok"},{"pid":"1f901a19c40d1a52a0b372cfd751d2e981918ab2","tid":520151,"uid":76318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伯母話唔洗幫手洗既話，係應該堅持去洗定聽佢話坐低睇電視</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會話 咁我幫你抹好冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5311569a9c3a7ba61ffc74e1830abafa9a1e43a2","tid":520151,"uid":13892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"以前上親ex屋企食飯，我想幫手都無得幫<br />\n次次俾ex媽咪勒令我坐低睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一一次幫過手好似都只係拎碟菜出廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會覺得應該主動提出幫手囉，都係種禮貌<br />\n雖然話過門都係客，但人地買餸煮飯招待你，禮尚往來都好應該"},{"pid":"69a2f3b6c7097bcb8a7e3ebf85fc1f478e1fe3f5","tid":520151,"uid":50253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"過門係客<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c4b218631fc18e491c3fd9d1ab84f8722a5e27e2","tid":520151,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a067aea46da5b8b0951c59b66d442dd2192357","tid":520151,"uid":61917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"男朋友媽咪請埋我上去打邊爐<br />\n同佢一齊買餸<br />\n不過我都係幫手執台開台 <br />\n我話我洗碗佢叫我唔好掂 <br />\n等第時教我摸熟個廚房先搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"第時就要做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2a05a9f95abc5613b5200242915d022b3def28","tid":520151,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"識做就會問我幫手洗<br />\n一來對你印象加分<br />\n二來多數都會話唔洗你洗架啦"},{"pid":"7371019a420f2a16325661d453401866bf5eec21","tid":520151,"uid":26728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"洗左，結果比男朋友鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c561096ac7170474745b91aadaefc76471b533a7","tid":520151,"uid":46700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"華人社會：做吓門面功夫，客套說話都要講<br />\n西人：問洗唔洗幫手，佢話唔洗就真係唔洗"},{"pid":"b750bd72a050d54702cdba6ceccc545735a2b1e4","tid":520151,"uid":3933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"90b4e1ad083fda4af4867a3d4067379ccfb751c6","tid":520151,"uid":41718,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啦，基本禮貌都無<br />\n人地煮埋飯俾你食，洗個碗好撚難？你當人地係奴隸？搵埋錢買埋送煮埋俾你食仲要執埋手尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"靠你老母開飯咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70e0e33e65af7a0f5251071bdeb16d60b8e2db3","tid":520151,"uid":38550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n就算想獻殷勤都唔應該直接落指示俾工人<br />\n個工人係人地o既工人<br />\n指示人地個工人係喧賓奪主適得其反<br />\n<br />\n想洗最多同主人家講<br />\n但正常主人家都會推卻<br />\n你去搵下第二啲嘢做例如切下生果搬下檯檯櫈櫈再唔係吹下水咪算囉"},{"pid":"7a70bd4387974bfcfd5b6bfc18d0c0f87fd3782c","tid":520151,"uid":33944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"頭3次去男朋友屋企食飯都會同佢一齊入去洗碗<br />\n跟住到宜家大概10次先會洗1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172d49eace7292523ded8020f3d306ee96f46b4d","tid":520151,"uid":91767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:47:17.000Z","msg":"你同我諗法一樣。過門都係客，應該好好招待客人，有咩理由叫客人洗碗啦呀？仲要有工人，咁工人要嚟做咩呀?"},{"pid":"856f7a4c4e977b2426e1fb626899fd464cc4a6c4","tid":520151,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦 當你係客 唔洗當你自己人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁而家的而且確係客喎! 根本唔係自己人。就算係自己人，都冇理由要去洗啦，屋企有工人。"},{"pid":"789cde958d1155eac3977b9c6383e0f4d7b90321","tid":520151,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"唔洗，直接入房扑嘢就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1250b054f6d0f62801d6771bc0d0d12378378efc","tid":520151,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗，直接入房扑嘢就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪係囉，人哋有畀你屌㗎嘛，仲要人幫手洗碗? 如果要洗，咁就取消扑野呢個項目喇。"},{"pid":"581f7522825104d40e118669465e5d9810f10fe4","tid":520151,"uid":45817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"幫伯母洗碗一定會加分，基本野<br />\n但有工人就唔洗啦"},{"pid":"5472ac757d1e948213db2fd14b0911781253aa6d","tid":520151,"uid":45817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"791dfbf2b0eb460b09c1282c3837e329a7d8952d","tid":520151,"uid":66945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"上親去食飯都冇洗過<br />\n因為次次食嗰陣啲野攤喺枱面等到我走都未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係等緊你執"},{"pid":"6da829c42e35a5c1c21549c156cfc3d629556f97","tid":520151,"uid":56626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"正常應該係咁：<br />\n<br />\n你話伯母等我幫手洗碗啦<br />\n通常伯母都會話唔洗啦你去睇電視啦<br />\n咁你就可以出返去<br />\n<br />\n如果佢好唔客氣咁話好呀<br />\n你男朋友就應該入去廚房同你一齊洗"},{"pid":"823c1f3100fb9805da669a0f9c0fc50ba3a68563","tid":520151,"uid":38188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常應該係咁：<br />\n<br />\n你話伯母等我幫手洗碗啦<br />\n通常伯母都會話唔洗啦你去睇電視啦<br />\n咁你就可以出返去<br />\n<br />\n如果佢好唔客氣咁話好呀<br />\n你男朋友就應該入去廚房同你一齊洗</blockquote><br />\n啱啊，唔好理咩客唔客先，如果真係有心嫁入去或者娶人個女，呢啲細節位真係加分扣分，而且就算真係要洗，咪同另一半一齊洗當情趣囉！"},{"pid":"82b6b93e9900043acf4d1af3af00bb4c838f7739","tid":520151,"uid":116752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"正常第一次大家都客客氣氣點會要個女仔洗<br />\n我ex個媽咪 想執下枱都唔俾 叫我坐定定<br />\n依家男朋友媽咪食完飯即刻離開張枱 咁咪我洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從此之後我冇上過去lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e964f93e7ce94e9e8679157a8b46725977c9989","tid":520151,"uid":116752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"其實洗下碗幾咁閒 <br />\n又唔係日日上黎食飯<br />\n不過想要返少少尊重同禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1749a376f1bc5db4bf933a89b17cdf8f4881c5b6","tid":520151,"uid":81575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"有工人姐姐硬係唔洗自己洗啦"},{"pid":"18449d22224113b2c695974c8739d6adc702494d","tid":520151,"uid":1964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"我男朋友喺屋企有幫手洗開碗<br />\n我第一次上去嗰日，佢同我講陣間要一齊洗碗<br />\n食完飯佢同auntie講&rdquo;阿媽，隊長夫人想幫你洗碗&rdquo;<br />\n入到去佢同我講碗佢洗就得，我剩係幫手抹下碗就得<br />\n其實要我洗我ok既，我最後都話同佢一人洗一半<br />\n不過我好開心男朋友識平衡兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc249f4f186d3518ffb0eba31cd0c428cc7c1582","tid":520151,"uid":14337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"未嫁唔洗啦<br />\n嫁左先洗"},{"pid":"ebad78faa939bf88ae184810b832ac15ef3b9706","tid":520151,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"洗碗咁少嘢，梗係拖埋地，抹埋窗，最好洗埋廁所咁就very good<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}